    "core": {
      "name": "Core",
      "definition": "The actively managed conviction book \u2014 structural Exponential Age and Universal Code positions held with intent but actioned on the technicals (DeMark exhaustion, regression bands). Usually full cycle trades (2 years to 5 years) Trimmed, closed, or added as the charts dictate while the thesis stands. These are the bulk of the risk taking and are sized as such (larger, high conviction but adjust for volatility of underlying to meet your risk tolerance).",
